Package: ggfacet
Type: Package
Title: Handy Facetting for ggplot2
Version: 1.0
Author: Raphael Scherrer
Maintainer: Raphael Scherrer <r.scherrer@rug.nl> <raphael.scherrer@evobio.eu>
Description: Wrapper around ggplot2's facetting functions that allow splitting
    plots into facets with customized strip labels, including with parsed text 
    such as mathematical notation.
